  "text": "Single-molecule force spectroscopy experiments were performed using an Asylum MFP-3D AFM (Asylum Research, Santa Barbara, CA), using silicon nitride cantilevers with spring constants in the range 40.28 ± 1.28 pN nm −1 (Bruker, CA). Cantilever spring constants were calibrated in buffer using the equipartition theorem [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
